{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-static-folders","description":"Lets you add additional static folders","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"imdaveead","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/79380ffa51fbcc290addff599ad23604"},"repository":null,"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-static-folders\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-static-folders\" aria-label=\"gatsby plugin static folders permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-static-folders</h1>\n<p>Lets you add additional static folders to your site, to better organize it.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  plugins: [\n    {\n      resolve: &#39;gatsby-plugin-static-folders&#39;,\n      options: {\n        folders: [\n          &#39;./images&#39;,\n          &#39;./downloads&#39;,\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>This will merge the two folders <code class=\"language-text\">images</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">downloads</code> into the output <code class=\"language-text\">public</code> folder.</p>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-static-folders/","id":"ed834fc0-57c4-5a43-b70a-8f90c5754f3c","layout":"plugins"}}